${font size=7}${color slate grey}Now Playing $hr${color }${font }
Artist: ${alignr}${mpd_artist}
Title: ${alignr}${mpd_title 35}
Album: ${alignr}${mpd_album}
$mpd_bar
$mpd_elapsed/$mpd_length ${alignc}$mpd_status ${alignr}$mpd_percent%
